For the thousands who fled Ukraine at the start of the war, life has changed dramatically over the past four years. CNNs Danny Freeman spoke to Kate Sobolevska, a young woman in Philadelphia who came to the US as a timid teenager and is now thriving despite the adversity in her homeland.
